</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Police investigating cult-linked deaths said the bodies of a Swiss man, a
British-born woman and a baby found in a burnt-out house in Quebec were
probably murdered. In Switzerland, the scene of other deaths, warrants were
issued for cult leader Luc Jouret and an associate.
