profits from Pounds 1.81m to Pounds 1.29m at Novo Group in the year ended
March 31.
Sales rose 19 per cent to Pounds 17.1m (Pounds 14.3m).
The group is involved in litigation concerning Walport International, which
was acquired from BET, concerning certain alleged licensing and copyright
irregularities.
